Download steamcmd.

$ wget https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/client/installer/steamcmd_linux.tar.gz

Extract it into its own directory somwhere in $HOME

Put gzw_verify.txt and update_gzw.sh from this archive into that same directory
(where steamcmd.sh is.)

Read carefully and edit both gzw_verify.txt and  update_gzw.sh for Steam 
directory paths, home user path, and Steam username/passwords.

Run ./update_gzw.sh

If using Steam authenticator, you will have to approve login on mobile device.

Credit to @Wifiik_CZ on GZW Discord.
